# Skill Editing Conventions

When creating or editing skills:

1. Every skill directory MUST have a `SKILL.md` with YAML frontmatter containing `name` and `description`
2. The `description` field should clearly state WHEN to trigger and WHEN NOT to trigger
3. Reference documents go in `references/` subdirectory
4. Templates and static resources go in `assets/` subdirectory
5. Executable scripts go in `scripts/` subdirectory
6. Skills in `skills-experimental/` must include a warning about their experimental status
